{"tid":1624210,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一國兩制下，普選都係冇撚用","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:25:42.000Z","uid":79957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b6befd338fcade6cc3773306e03d337c0a0e39b","tid":1624210,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:13:38.000Z","msg":"大家要醒喇<br />\n即使係以前中共對香港冇咁強勢嘅時候<br />\n一樣有地區直選、一人一票嘅區議會<br />\n但大家可以維基查下建制同泛民嘅議席比例<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建制327席</span></span> 對 <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">泛民124席</span></span><br />\n政治篩選、種票、掌心雷、蛇齋餅糭、遺失選民資料數得出嘅都有<br />\n<br />\n同國家機器一齊玩選舉，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一定係收皮</span></strong></span><br />\n要避免，就係要獨立<br />\n唔好發夢一國兩制下嘅任何民主會係民主<br />\n<br />\n一定有人會反駁而家冇民意支持獨立，未係時候<br />\n但只要認清上述事實，相信獨立，將呢個思想係呢到開始燃點，散播出去，造就民意，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立先會有曙光</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家記住我地嘅意見都係民意<br />\n我地可以打破香港人對以暴制暴嘅政治潔癖，<br />\n點解唔可以打破埋提倡獨立嘅心理關口？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民覺醒，香港獨立</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廷伸閱讀：<br />\n<strong>瑞士模式港獨 &mdash; 中港雙贏、中立方案的再提出</strong><br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%99%E8%B4%8F-%E4%B8%AD%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E7%9A%84%E5%86%8D%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259B%2599%25E8%25B4%258F-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2587%25BA%2F&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=0f1b10ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259B%2599%25E8%25B4%258F-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2587%25BA%2F&h=ca098f72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%99%E8%B4%8F-%E4%B8%AD%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E7%9A%84%E5%86%8D%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA/</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">構思香港如何獨立、獨立之後如何定義國體及與周邊大國關係，可參考瑞士模式而有所損益，其中當然是以與中國的關係為核心考慮。一個合理而有利的方案可包括下列各點：\n\n&middot; 香港成為主權獨立及無武裝永久中立國，並同時成為聯合國一員；\n\n&middot; 香港的獨立中立地位由中國單方面向國際社會承諾，並由美、英、加、澳、日及任何其他國家確認（或可直接由中國及這些國家簽署國際條約一次過確立）；\n\n&middot; 獨立的香港永久不結盟；\n\n&middot; 獨立的香港採取完全符合《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》的自由民主體制，國家領導人和立法會由開放提名及公民一人一票產生；\n\n&middot; 獨立的香港與中國之間的法域關係裏，嚴格永久保留並加強現存對中國的不引渡、不遣解規定；\n\n&middot; 獨立的香港以憲法威力永久廢除死刑。</code></pre>"},{"pid":"2e5873fd7bf73685b822fd0b455115b6ab7343d3","tid":1624210,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:18:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90ae864e18f503a8a479bedca2fe15442f956e3b","tid":1624210,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:22:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22d899dd43760edcfbfe97e313a94ecf3eb2dd29","tid":1624210,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:25:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7260c824388d067676153a763e6a25ed056ff1e","tid":1624210,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"237a6ea8d2c96adb2baa01714ab7ef58fbb455bf","tid":1624210,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:34:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f9c57649655ce1bdb4dddd797131777981f9901","tid":1624210,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"推"}]}